      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6675669/" class="title-link">张之洞与戊戌变法</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6675669"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2568276/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2568276-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2568276/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">周绍纲</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-05-20"
      class="main-meta">2014-05-20 13:53:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6675669_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   周绍纲        1894年，中日甲午战争爆发。次年，以北洋水师全军覆没，清廷割地赔款而告终。当时朝野震惊，纷纷要求变法图强。3年后，岁在戊戌，6月11日，光绪帝颁布《定国是诏》，决定变法，史称“百日维新”。维新历时不过103天，却影响了近代中国的百年进程。对这场“失去...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6675669_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6675669_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










